									<h5 id="subject_146173">
										<a href="http://fantasy-faction.com/forum/(jun-2016)-random-wikipedia-article/(jun-2016)-random-wikipedia-article-submission-thread/msg146173/#msg146173" rel="nofollow">Re: [Jun 2016] - Random Wikipedia Article - Submission Thread</a>
									</h5>
									<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>Reply #2 on:</strong> June 21, 2016, 02:56:03 AM &#187;</div>
									<div id="msg_146173_quick_mod"></div>
								</div>
