									<h5 id="subject_146996">
										<a href="http://fantasy-faction.com/forum/(jun-2016)-random-wikipedia-article/(jun-2016)-random-wikipedia-article-submission-thread/msg146996/#msg146996" rel="nofollow">Re: [Jun 2016] - Random Wikipedia Article - Submission Thread</a>
									</h5>
									<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>Reply #8 on:</strong> June 30, 2016, 08:38:48 PM &#187;</div>
									<div id="msg_146996_quick_mod"></div>
